title: Tyson Apostol Breaks Down 'The Challenge: USA' Final | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Tyson Apostol joins Johnny this week to talk about all the controversy surrounding the final challenge of ‘The Challenge: USA’ and his own experiences running it.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Tyson Apostol
Producers: Sasha Ashall and Jessie Lopez
